<Paragraph Style="{DynamicResource HeaderParagraphStyle}"><Bold>
	Relation and Hierarchy</Bold>
</Paragraph>

<Paragraph>
The Grouping control also supports manipulation of data with hierarchical relationships and nested tables. Changes to any data element automatically update the grid and the position of the changed records appropriately. New rows may be added at any level.
</Paragraph> 
<Paragraph> <Bold>Foreign-Key Reference Demo</Bold> - This sample retrieves the data manipulated from a foreign-key-reference relation between tables.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph> <Bold>List-Item Reference Demo</Bold> - Illustrates the list-item reference relation between the data tables.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph> <Bold>Master-Detail Demo</Bold> - Demonstrates how to manually specify master-detail relations between different tables.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph> <Bold>Strong-Typed Collection Demo</Bold> - This sample features the bounded custom collection to the hierarchical grid.</Paragraph>
</FlowDocument> 
